<div class="d-panels font-secondary-light">
<div id="aip_a" class="d-panel p" style="display: none">
<div class="p" id="aff1">
<sup>1</sup>Sidney Kimmel Medical College at Thomas Jefferson University, Department of Orthopaedics Surgery, Philadelphia, PA, USA</div>
