<div class="fn" id="cor">
<sup>✉</sup><p class="display-inline">Corresponding Author: Surena Namdari, Rothman Institute, Thomas Jefferson University, Shoulder &amp; Elbow Surgery, Philadelphia, PA, USA, Email: surena.namdari@rothmaninstitute.com</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="anp_a" class="d-panel p" style="display: none"><div class="notes p"><section id="historyarticle-meta1" class="history"><p>Received 2017 Nov 28; Accepted 2018 Feb 4; Issue date 2018 Jul.</p></section></div></div>
<div id="clp_a" class="d-panel p" style="display: none">
<div>2018 © BY THE ARCHIVES OF BONE AND JOINT SURGERY</div>
<div class="p"><a href="/about/copyright/" class="usa-link">PMC Copyright notice</a></div>
</div>
